Description:

Fitness to Practice is an album produced for charity by Dr. Adam Kay and Dr. Suman Biswas (a.k.a. Amateur Transplants) in 2004. The album is published on the Friday Audio label of The Friday Project. The album contains extremely strong language and therefore, according to the official website, "should not be bought for an elderly maiden aunt."
